// TRNSLATE is a text-based lump in ZDoom that defines custom color translations
// (color remapping). These translations can be applied to actors, sprites, 
// and overlays, allowing their palette colors to be remapped dynamically, 
// including at runtime.

// https://zdoom.org/w/index.php?title=TRNSLATE

Red		= "0:255=176:191"
Green	= "0:255=112:127"
Blue	= "0:255=192:207"